  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\n`Error: VM Exception while processing transaction: invalid opcode` when calling `msg.sender.transfer` that should not be happening. Contract code has been manually tested in Ethereum Wallet against Ropsten and found to work.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nIn a fresh Truffle project, paste this into a file `tests/TestNonsense.sol`:\r\n\r\n```\r\npragma solidity ^0.4.2;\r\n\r\nimport \"truffle/Assert.sol\";\r\n\r\ncontract Ledger {\r\n  mapping(address => uint) balances;\r\n\r\n  function Ledger() payable {\r\n    balances[msg.sender] = msg.value;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  function withdraw() {\r\n    var balance = balances[msg.sender];\r\n    balances[msg.sender] = 0;\r\n    msg.sender.transfer(balance); // VM Exception here.\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  // This one won't fail because it doesn't attempt a transfer.\r\n  function withdrawWithoutTransfer() {\r\n    var balance = balances[msg.sender];\r\n    balances[msg.sender] = 0;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  function deposit() payable {\r\n    balances[msg.sender] += msg.value;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\ncontract TestNonsense {\r\n  uint public initialBalance = 5 ether;\r\n  Ledger public ledger;\r\n\r\n  // Does not have error.\r\n  function testDeposit() {\r\n    ledger = new Ledger();\r\n    ledger.deposit.value(1 ether)();\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  // Also no error.\r\n  function testWithdrawWithoutTransfer() {\r\n    ledger = new Ledger();\r\n    ledger.deposit.value(1 ether)();\r\n    ledger.withdrawWithoutTransfer();\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  // Invalid opcode even though the contract function works in Ethereum Wallet.\r\n  function testWithdraw() {\r\n    ledger = new Ledger();\r\n    ledger.deposit.value(1 ether)();\r\n    ledger.withdraw();\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThen start up testrpc and run `truffle test test/TestNonsense.sol`.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nAll tests pass without VM Exception.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\n```\r\nTestNonsense\r\n    ✓ testDeposit (43ms)\r\n    ✓ testWithdrawWithoutTransfer (39ms)\r\n    1) testWithdraw\r\n    > No events were emitted\r\n\r\n\r\n  2 passing (1s)\r\n  1 failing\r\n\r\n  1) TestNonsense testWithdraw:\r\n     Error: VM Exception while processing transaction: invalid opcode\r\n      at Object.InvalidResponse (/Users/joel/.asdf/installs/nodejs/8.1.2/.npm/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:37295:16)\r\n      at /Users/joel/.asdf/installs/nodejs/8.1.2/.npm/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:224765:36\r\n      at /Users/joel/.asdf/installs/nodejs/8.1.2/.npm/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:208348:9\r\n      at XMLHttpRequest.request.onreadystatechange (/Users/joel/.asdf/installs/nodejs/8.1.2/.npm/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:209773:13)\r\n      at XMLHttpRequestEventTarget.dispatchEvent (/Users/joel/.asdf/installs/nodejs/8.1.2/.npm/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:67130:18)\r\n      at XMLHttpRequest._setReadyState (/Users/joel/.asdf/installs/nodejs/8.1.2/.npm/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:67420:12)\r\n      at XMLHttpRequest._onHttpResponseEnd (/Users/joel/.asdf/installs/nodejs/8.1.2/.npm/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:67575:12)\r\n      at IncomingMessage.<anonymous> (/Users/joel/.asdf/installs/nodejs/8.1.2/.npm/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:67535:24)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: OS X\r\n* Truffle version: Truffle v3.4.9 (core: 3.4.8), Solidity v0.4.15 (solc-js)\r\n* Ethereum client: EthereumJS TestRPC v4.1.1\r\n* node version: v8.1.2\r\n* npm version: 5.0.3\r\n",
